Class ActivityItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.module.aim.helper.ActivityItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ActivityItem>

    public class ActivityItem
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ActivityItem>
    Activity helper bean. Used to store activity data in more user friendly way. Also suports converting Activity to XML for Ajax like use or any other use.
